# nusaOS Authors and Contributors

This document lists the individuals who have contributed to the nusaOS 
operating system. nusaOS is an evolved project that builds upon the 
foundation of its predecessor, duckOS.

## Original Author (duckOS)
* byteduck - Lead Developer of the original duckOS base.
    GitHub: https://github.com/byteduck

## Current Lead Maintainer (nusaOS)
* Danko / Dava (@danko1122q) - Lead Developer responsible for the 
    transformation, feature expansion, and ongoing evolution into nusaOS.
    GitHub: https://github.com/danko1122q

## Contributors
* The open-source community members who have submitted pull requests 
    and bug reports.

